components.name: AppLayoutComponent
components.templateData:
<mdtx-layout [progressValue]="100" [rightSidenavIcon]="rightSidenavIcon">
  <!-- Toolbar Left-->
  <ng-template mdtxToolbarLeft>
    {{ title.getTitle() }}
    <mdtx-navlist [items]="toolbarLeft" [inToolbar]="true"></mdtx-navlist
  ></ng-template>

  <!-- Toolbar Right -->
  <ng-template mdtxToolbarRight
    ><mdtx-navlist [items]="toolbarRight" [inToolbar]="true"></mdtx-navlist
  ></ng-template>

  <!-- Toolbar Center -->
  <ng-template mdtxToolbarCenter
    ><mdtx-navlist [items]="toolbarCenter" [inToolbar]="true"></mdtx-navlist
  ></ng-template>

  <!-- Statubar Left  -->
  <ng-template mdtxStatusbarLeft
    ><mdtx-navlist [items]="statusbarLeft" [inToolbar]="true"></mdtx-navlist
  ></ng-template>

  <!-- Statubar Rigth  -->
  <ng-template mdtxStatusbarRight>
    <mdtx-navlist [items]="statusbarRight" [inToolbar]="true"></mdtx-navlist>
  </ng-template>

  <!-- Statubar Center  -->
  <ng-template mdtxStatusbarCenter
    ><mdtx-navlist [items]="statusbarCenter" [inToolbar]="true"></mdtx-navlist
  ></ng-template>

  <!-- Sidenav Left Top -->
  <ng-template mdtxSidenavLeftTop
    ><mdtx-navlist [items]="sidenavLeftTop"></mdtx-navlist
  ></ng-template>

  <!-- Sidenav Left Center -->
  <ng-template mdtxSidenavLeftCenter
    ><mdtx-navlist [items]="sidenavLeftCenter"></mdtx-navlist
  ></ng-template>

  <!-- Sidenav Left Bottom -->
  <ng-template mdtxSidenavLeftBottom
    ><mdtx-navlist [items]="sidenavLeftBottom"></mdtx-navlist
  ></ng-template>

  <!-- Sidenav Right Top -->
  <ng-template mdtxSidenavRightTop
    ><mdtx-navlist [items]="sidenavRightTop"></mdtx-navlist
  ></ng-template>

  <!-- Sidenav Right Center -->
  <ng-template mdtxSidenavRightCenter
    ><mdtx-navlist [items]="sidenavRightCenter"></mdtx-navlist
  ></ng-template>

  <!-- Sidenav Right Right -->
  <ng-template mdtxSidenavRightBottom>
    <mdtx-navlist [items]="sidenavRightBottom"> </mdtx-navlist
  ></ng-template>

  <!-- Content Center Left -->
  <ng-template
    mdtxContentCenterLeft
    *ngIf="contentCenterLeft && contentCenterLeft.length > 0"
  >
    <mdtx-sidebar [topToolbarItems]="contentCenterLeft"></mdtx-sidebar>
  </ng-template>

  <!-- Content Center Right -->
  <ng-template
    mdtxContentCenterRight
    *ngIf="contentCenterRight && contentCenterRight.length > 0"
  >
    <mdtx-sidebar [topToolbarItems]="contentCenterRight"></mdtx-sidebar>
  </ng-template>

  <!-- Content Center  -->
  <ng-template mdtxContentCenter>
    <router-outlet></router-outlet>
  </ng-template>
</mdtx-layout>

components.name: InputAutocompleteComponent
components.templateData:
<mat-form-field class="example-full-width">
  <mat-label> {{ label || inputName | titlecase }}</mat-label>
  <input
    type="text"
    #mdtxInput="mdtxInput"
    mdtxInput
    matInput
    [formControl]="inputControl"
    [matAutocomplete]="auto"
    [attr.data-testid]="testid()"
  />
  <mat-autocomplete
    autoActiveFirstOption
    #auto="matAutocomplete"
    [displayWith]="displayWith"
    [autoSelectActiveOption]="true"
  >
    @for (option of filteredOptions$ | async ; track option) {
    <mat-option [value]="valueWith(option)">{{ option.name }}</mat-option>
    }
    <mat-option [value]="null">None</mat-option>
  </mat-autocomplete>

  <!-- Prefix icon -->
  @if(prefixIcon){
  <mat-icon matPrefix [color]="iconColor()">{{ prefixIcon }}</mat-icon>
  }

  <!-- Typing indicator -->
  <mat-icon matSuffix [color]="iconColor()">
    @if(mdtxInput.isTyping()){
    <mat-progress-spinner
      [diameter]="22"
      mode="indeterminate"
    ></mat-progress-spinner>
    }
  </mat-icon>
</mat-form-field>

propertiesClass.name: dateRange

components.templateData:
<mat-form-field>
  <mat-label>{{ label || inputName | titlecase }}</mat-label>

  <mat-date-range-input
    #mdtxInput="mdtxInput"
    mdtxInput
    [formGroup]="dateRange"
    [rangePicker]="dateRangePicker"
    [comparisonStart]="dateRange.value.start"
    [comparisonEnd]="dateRange.value.end"
  >
    <input
      matStartDate
      [placeholder]="startDateLabel"
      formControlName="start"
      [attr.data-testid]="testid()"
    />
    <input
      matEndDate
      [placeholder]="endDateLabel"
      formControlName="end"
      [attr.data-testid]="testid()"
    />
  </mat-date-range-input>

  <!-- Prefix icon -->
  @if(prefixIcon){
  <mat-icon matPrefix [color]="iconColor()">{{ prefixIcon }}</mat-icon>
  }

  <!-- Typing indicator -->
  <mat-icon matSuffix [color]="iconColor()">
    @if(mdtxInput.isTyping()){
    <mat-progress-spinner
      [diameter]="22"
      mode="indeterminate"
    ></mat-progress-spinner>
    }
  </mat-icon>

  <mat-datepicker-toggle
    matIconSuffix
    [for]="dateRangePicker"
  ></mat-datepicker-toggle>
  <mat-date-range-picker #dateRangePicker></mat-date-range-picker>
</mat-form-field>
